<span id="freeTextContainer12325458228646159295">Holy crap this book sucked. Read this only if you like listening to people endlessly abusing one another. Keep reading if you like overuse of pointless images. I like magical realism, but I kept waiting for there to be some sort of larger theme or something to tie everything together, and instead, the book just reaches the last page. It doesn&apos;t end, it doesn&apos;t stop, there&apos;s just a last page. Totally, totally lame. I wish I&apos;d stopped listening at the beginning when I&apos;d considered it.</span>
  <span id="freeText12325458228646159295" style="display:none">Holy crap this book sucked. Read this only if you like listening to people endlessly abusing one another. Keep reading if you like overuse of pointless images. I like magical realism, but I kept waiting for there to be some sort of larger theme or something to tie everything together, and instead, the book just reaches the last page. It doesn't end, it doesn't stop, there's just a last page. Totally, totally lame. I wish I'd stopped listening at the beginning when I'd considered it.</span>
