      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/6423549-of-bees-and-mist">Quotes from Of Bees and Mist</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;You don't seem to understand me,' she said. 'The last thing I want is to start over. You can't wake up something that's dead and buried.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
